From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mohammad Ebrahim Rahimbeiky <rahimbeiky@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 22:00:00 +0400
Subject: [PATCH] Wire combat knockback profile into NMS

Routes melee knockback, sprint-hit velocity, projectile launch and impact,
fishing hook impact, and explosion velocity through the combat profile. This
patch is intentionally ordered immediately after ProjectileCollideEvent because
later PandaSpigot patches change several of these same files.

